Craster's Wife 1 (Oathkeeper)028120siy9as6ghj6e98m0wybgv5u1b0738271663962014-11-28T10:38:01ZSer Patrek25358400Undo revision 166394 by [[Special:Contributions/Brother Crow|Brother Crow]] ([[User talk:Brother Crow|talk]])'''A wife of Craster''' is an unnamed minor character in the fourth season. She is played by Kristy Robinson and debuts in &quot;Oathkeeper&quot;.

In OathKeeper she's the first of the wives to be seen saying &quot;Gift to the Gods&quot; and the one who lowers her head when Karl tells them to &quot;Shut Up&quot;

She returns in &quot;First of His Name&quot; for the burning of Craster's Keep
